videos.headline: New Mexico St. QB honors father with four-TD game
videos.description: New Mexico State's Andrew Allen joins SportsCenter to talk about attending his father's funeral service on Saturday and driving four hours to be with his teammates and play against Louisiana-Lafayette, throwing four touchdown passes in a 37-34 victory.
